9:{"metadata":[["$","title","0",{"children":"The Ghost Game | Global Drama Verse Guide"}],["$","meta","1",{"name":"description","content":"Aspiring YouTuber Gi-ho stages a fake seance for viral content, but Ja-young joins, seeking her missing sister Seo-woo. In an underground cistern, Seo-woo volunteers as the \"possessed,\" but when she collapses, terror unfolds. Trapped with sinister forces, the students face a deadly fate, leading to a shocking twist."}],["$","meta","2",{"name":"keywords","content":"KDrama,Anime,TV Series,Movies,Global Drama,Drama Guide,Watch Online"}],["$","meta","3",{"name":"robots","content":"index, follow"}],["$","link","4",{"rel":"canonical","href":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/movies/107847/the-ghost-game"}],["$","meta","5",{"property":"og:title","content":"The Ghost Game"}],["$","meta","6",{"property":"og:description","content":"Aspiring YouTuber Gi-ho stages a fake seance for viral content, but Ja-young joins, seeking her missing sister Seo-woo. In an underground cistern, Seo-woo volunteers as the \"possessed,\" but when she collapses, terror unfolds. Trapped with sinister forces, the students face a deadly fate, leading to a shocking twist."}],["$","meta","7",{"property":"og:url","content":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/movies/107847/the-ghost-game"}],["$","meta","8",{"property":"og:image","content":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/6uF6PnY1gWNmDkAMYO1qhgdgozM.jpg"}],["$","meta","9",{"property":"og:type","content":"video.movie"}],["$","meta","10",{"name":"twitter:card","content":"summary_large_image"}],["$","meta","11",{"name":"twitter:title","content":"The Ghost Game"}],["$","meta","12",{"name":"twitter:description","content":"Aspiring YouTuber Gi-ho stages a fake seance for viral content, but Ja-young joins, seeking her missing sister Seo-woo. In an underground cistern, Seo-woo volunteers as the \"possessed,\" but when she collapses, terror unfolds. Trapped with sinister forces, the students face a deadly fate, leading to a shocking twist.